	<span style="font-size: 12px;">This jar of citronella maximum strength scented granules is for use in all oil burners. The citrus aromas from these top quality burning granules are truly wonderful and long lasting. Citronella is said to be the best known natural insect repellent whilst granules are less hassle and easier to use than oils. These gorgeous simmering granules are packed in large amber glass jars that hold 130g of this wonderful product. The amber jar prolongs the aroma and colour&nbsp;and prevents&nbsp;worry about splitting plastic bags. To use simply place one or more teaspoons into the well of your burner and light the candle underneath &ndash; no need to add water. The granules then heat and will simmer away slowly releasing a wonderful and long lasting aroma that will fill your room. After use, just shake the used and cooled granules into a bin and replenish as needed. Why not check out our range of fantastic oil burners?</span></p>
